{"tid":1689093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 ，反抗 咁反抗未阿？","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T16:55:44.000Z","uid":12184,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"93230fa47fcda4508fdfc8d810407a5af4cc724d","tid":1689093,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"今日又有一堆人出嚟講好嬲好嬲<br />\n<br />\n嬲撚完未呀,幾時先捨得將自己思維升級或者轉職做勇武呀<br />\n勇武手足又一開始揸住把遮妹下妹下<br />\n到而家識整各種魔法<br />\n<br />\n其他人就日日喺度好嬲好嬲又唔做野，咩都驚<br />\n你肯升級，就幫到更多手，就更小人被捕<br />\n見到啲乜嘢被捕提堂po就喺度話乜嘢辛苦曬喊撚咗<br />\n<br />\n你哋自己有份做成㗎<br />\n<br />\n我唔係放負，係想講，想贏，就要升級，升級先會令到個垃圾政府跪。<br />\n<br />\n想贏唔係得把口，係要行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日七區阿</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日七區阿</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日七區阿</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聽日七區阿</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"880b13be1ba4bad547a08453efda1d7068d4f4b6","tid":1689093,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"795a45986b26a64472b7e92f4f8d720ce3a76663","tid":1689093,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d780f04cee27f3eaef182e46389fa2c8220911","tid":1689093,"uid":12184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795a45986b26a64472b7e92f4f8d720ce3a76663","tid":1689093,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"無，我絕對無 <br />\n我只係要更多人醒"},{"pid":"95b694c769ab